_:ref_07d30a2c93964b35 a oc:WorkflowStep ;
    dcterms:description "Check for common analytical pitfalls: join explosion, survivorship bias, incomplete periods, denominator shifting, average of averages, timezone mismatches, selection bias, and other statistical traps" ;
